---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Sujan Kapadia - Chief AI Officer at Chariot Solutions">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
        About Me
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm the Chief AI Officer at Chariot Solutions, where I help organizations
          understand and harness AI to transform how they build software and serve their customers.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
          My journey in technology spans over two decades, from building distributed systems
          with Scala and Akka to now focusing on the frontier of AI agents and developer tools.
          I'm passionate about the intersection of human creativity and machine intelligence.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
          When I'm not exploring the latest in AI, you'll find me speaking at conferences,
          mentoring developers, or working on side projects that push the boundaries of
          what's possible with modern tooling.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-6">
          Current Focus Areas
        </h2>

        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-500 mt-1">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong>AI Agents:</strong> Building and deploying autonomous coding assistants</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-500 mt-1">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong>Developer Tools:</strong> Creating tools that augment human capabilities</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-500 mt-1">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong>AI Strategy:</strong> Helping organizations navigate the AI landscape</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-500 mt-1">&#9679;</span>
            <span><strong>Human-AI Collaboration:</strong> Exploring how humans and AI work together</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200"
        >
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
